{"tid":280621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"時代力量澄清從未接觸過涉旺角騷亂少女","createTime":"2017-06-12T08:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T14:22:39.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87e599e88806a2c08ab950c1917f2fe74ed4a4bc","tid":280621,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:15:55.000Z","msg":"有報道引述台灣時代力量立委黃國昌指，因參與旺角騷亂而被控暴動罪的18歲香港女子李倩怡，目前正在台灣，獲人權團體照顧。<br />\n<br />\n時代力量之後發聲明，指黃國昌在回應有關問題時，已表示自己不太清楚有關個案，據個人了解，似乎那位香港人由一些台灣的人權團體協助。<br />\n<br />\n時代力量秘書長陳惠敏接受本台查詢時，亦澄清從未接觸過李倩怡本人，也不肯定她是否人在台灣，只是聽說李倩怡曾接觸過一些台灣人權團體。"},{"pid":"b6a0a2b5e962a94d00e39e69fa027bd8d699b218","tid":280621,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:57:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"258cb83037044833a3281f833584ee0ccad1b6f5","tid":280621,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:07:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09e7ca1d38b54f33778b0171feddcdc0ddb715f2","tid":280621,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:19:37.000Z","msg":"係咪有警察去問佢地"},{"pid":"437711c1aa1893416607f411fa3b6af1507de2cc","tid":280621,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:45:19.000Z","msg":"應該怕比人爆出黎、到時會比人拉"},{"pid":"40d90098ae8bab38aa24a7b8454425b010af5af8","tid":280621,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:54:48.000Z","msg":"陳惠敏.jpg"},{"pid":"293bf2e04d0a8f4b93193844fac72646791d1060","tid":280621,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:56:46.000Z","msg":"屌 係唔出得街就私下講啦  又成撚日聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4539c8492897ad212c821f8e87acea71c29f294","tid":280621,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:27:48.000Z","msg":"俾人鎖定範圍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n柒到呢<br />\n<br />\n豬的隊友"},{"pid":"489089ae1359846dc6afdd7d20601d7f11c16bc4","tid":280621,